## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the inherent biases present in the sources. Some sources may have a specific focus or agenda, which could influence the interpretation of the data. Additionally, the rapidly changing nature of terrorism means that new threats and trends may emerge that are not covered in this report.